MODIFICATIONS:
--------------
This fork includes the following modifications:
- Updated to Gradle 8.10 (from 5.4.1)
- Updated to Kotlin 2.0.20 (from 1.3.50)
- Updated to Android SDK 35 (from 29)
- Updated to Java 17 (from 8)
- Updated to OkHttp 4.12.0 (from 3.12.0)
- Updated to Retrofit 2.11.0 (from 2.6.2)
- Updated all AndroidX and Kotlin dependencies to latest versions
- Fixed Moshi Kotlin reflection adapter configuration
- Removed deprecated kotlin-android-extensions plugin
- Fixed OkHttp 4.x API changes (setDispatcher -> dispatcher)
- Fixed nullability issues for modern Kotlin strict null-safety
- Updated all unit tests to work with Mockito 5.x
- Added GitHub Actions CI/CD configuration
- Commented out deprecated Maven publishing (for future migration)
- Disabled ktlint integration (for future reconfiguration)

